---
title: Shrimp & Lemon Risotto with Roasted Zucchini and Parmesan
description: This simple and elegant meal is perfect for a special occasion. Shrimp are tossed into a creamy risotto with a touch of lemon zest and Parmesan for kick. Perfectly roasted zucchini and butter make for a beautiful and delicious finish.
